| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3683 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ea5cf93-4e94-54b2-94d1-4050f2acdddb"
